reviews.headline: Leaves a film
reviews.comments: I have been using this product for 8 months. I loved the former version of this product which was more effective at removing makeup. This leaves a film on your lashes even after multiple rinses and following with a foaming cleanser after. The film transfers to my eyeballs overnight. I wake up with blurry vision. It only goes away after showering the next morning.

faceoff_positive.comments: I received this Mac hyper real fresh canvas cleansing oil as a complimentary sample. The cleansing oil comes in this glass bottle with w gold/yellow hue and the pump for it comes separately. Once inserted, I used one pump which was enough product to get all of my makeup off. The oil just melts away my make up and feels so nice and silky on my skin. It has a thin consistency and it spreads very well. After rubbing my face with it, it almost looks a bit soapy. It smells a bit like baby powder, but not quite as strong. It was quite pleasant. My skin felt so clean after washing it off and it was really obvious that all of my make up was removed. Even my mascara came off pretty easily, which is a lot to say as I've used other cleansing oils and they haven't performed as well in taking off my black mascara. With this, I didn't see any residue and my skin felt like a clean slate. I really love how this didn't dry out my skin at all and I didn't have to rub so hard to get the make up off. This also didn't cause any eye irritation, which some oil cleansers can cause. I also am really loving how little product is needed as it's a pretty decent sized bottle so I know it will last a while. The ingredients are also the biggest plus because it contains tsubaki, which is a very popular ingredient in Japan known for hydrating your skin. It also has oils such as jojoba and sunflower seed oil, which also have hydrating effects. This is major as it's not just about getting your make up off, but it also has skin benefits and won't strip off any hydration or cause damage to your skin barrier. I am extremely satisfied and highly recommend this. It is one of my favorites, if not my favorite, and I absolutely will add this to my routine.
